data.description: Breath taking panoramic views surrounds the home There is a lean to, ready for livestock. The spacious house is open with plenty of cabinets and counters in the kitchen. Master suite features double sinks, a walk-in closet, garden tub and is located at the opposite end of the home. Beautiful tongue and groove in the office. There is a 30x70 and a 36x30 shop situated on the same parcel as the home. Both shops are fully  over 3,000 sq ft fully finished shop space, this property is a true see.
